label: Neutral
short_description: Feet are perfectly parallel and pointing straight ahead. Baseline score.

label: Toes Out
short_description: Toes are angled outward. Opens the hips to engage inner thighs and inner calves.

label: Toes In
short_description: Toes are angled inward. Shifts focus to the outer sweeping muscles.

label: Heel Elevated
short_description: Heels are raised on plates or wedges. Drives knees forward to isolate the Quads.

label: Toes Elevated
short_description: Toes are raised on plates. Deepens the stretch in the calves and hamstrings.
